Core workflow concept DI_DataSpecs_Modelupdates_SN preserved across both versions with identical business purpose and agent functionality.
All three agents maintain identical descriptions and core responsibilities: technical specification creation, delta model changes, and functional test case generation.

Tool reference mechanism changed from direct tool names to empty references, potentially indicating incomplete migration or architectural change.
